{"tid":466253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因阻東方記者採訪兼搶機的連城廣場管理員巳被炒及永不錄用","createTime":"2017-11-12T11:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T14:13:00.000Z","uid":39539,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0332ff9f298161dd8a0ce98900ef77ed254382","tid":466253,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"《東方日報》記者日前在沙田連城廣場採訪時，遭連城廣場管理員阻止拍攝，甚至被強搶攝錄機及手機，事件引起社會各界關注。連城廣場為港鐵物業，港鐵發言人表示，涉事職員為外判保安員，港鐵了解事件後已即時將其開除，並已紀錄在案及永不錄用，強調港鐵對此類事件採取零容忍態度。 <br />\n<br />\n「搶機」事件發生於上周三（8日）中午，《東方日報》記者就黑客勒索事件在連城廣場縱橫遊分店門外採訪，以手提攝錄機拍攝期間，突然有3至4名自稱商場管理員上前阻止拍攝，聲稱︰「呢度唔准影相，要申請！」其中一名管理員更搶走記者手上的攝錄機及手機，並用身體迫記者退去走廊牆角位置。記者報警處理，警方到場調查後，對方交還手提攝錄機及手機，卻出言辱罵記者。記者已就有關事件到警署落口供，警方將案件列作求警調查，交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進，警方正調查案件，並蒐集證據。 <br />\n<br />\n阻撓《東方日報》記者採訪事件引起社會各界關注，立法會議員陸頌雄表示，《東方日報》採訪是發揮傳媒第四權，為市民知情權做事，任何正常新聞採訪都不應受干預，任何機構及團體都應尊重新聞自由，他促請警方盡快調查事件。 <br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強表示，即使拍攝的只是普通人，強搶攝錄機及手機已形同盜竊及搶劫，而記者採訪是為公眾權益，即使不想被採訪，有關人員亦無權強搶器材。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/192702_51cab9e031759cfa7dc66252a56ea15d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F192702_51cab9e031759cfa7dc66252a56ea15d.jpg&h=ad53dbb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e80849d1ecf96712d9024cebbac96af5f2dc6c4","tid":466253,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"港鐵你以為咁做百份就會放過你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97cbae6400087ba8767b7d884fce69b77ba1150","tid":466253,"uid":38293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白</span>"},{"pid":"8b9f8e5ae88552a43c069646db0931e1e0aa6982","tid":466253,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"老實說，mtr d員工，成日以為自己政府職員<br />\n臭串出名，咩部門都無分別<br />\n<br />\n利申，工作上見過"},{"pid":"0cecd2b910586400c589cfb35b3a46fc9e4f2c83","tid":466253,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">滑</span>"},{"pid":"0b5555d33578e53b6233c240cef7fe16562aa83a","tid":466253,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"因航表示歡迎<br />\n因鐵從此收皮"},{"pid":"88196b10579a9a915a5126a112a141cc73419542","tid":466253,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"因鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd965912b2039aa3677f74a47260d7b77b7fc90","tid":466253,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d39d7a06d09c705a99d49022124b2684f396364","tid":466253,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0a5c677625973ff18394d2be5b96fa09768aff","tid":466253,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d411fe75a97ff4d8a5b00d36f2a017fdb90db8b","tid":466253,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:16:12.000